name: Farm Invasion (m_enakeno, sydney06)
description:
Your farm has been invaded by birds, stop them before they destroy your crops. Once the crop meter reaches 0, it's game over.


  1. Use the eye button to look around
  2. Use the arrows to move around
  3. Double-tap on the bird to kill it
